# AI Resume Optimizer

An intelligent **AI-powered Resume Optimization System** built using **LangGraph + LLM (Groq)** that improves resumes based on job descriptions using an iterative feedback loop.

---

## Project Overview

This system analyzes a resume against a given job description, calculates an **ATS (Applicant Tracking System) score**, and improves the resume iteratively until it reaches a high-quality threshold.

---

## 🔁 Workflow

```text
Resume (PDF)
     ↓
Text Extraction
     ↓
ATS Evaluation
     ↓
 ┌───────────────┐
 ↓               ↓
Score ≥ 90     Score < 90
 ↓               ↓
 END        Improve Resume
                  ↓
            Re-evaluate 🔁
```

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

* Python 🐍
* LangGraph (workflow orchestration)
* LangChain
* Groq LLM (LLaMA 3.1)
* pdfplumber (PDF text extraction)
* python-dotenv

 Features

* 📄 Resume upload (PDF parsing)
* 🧠 Job Description Matching
* 📊 ATS Score Evaluation
* 🔍 Keyword Injection System
* 🔁 Iterative Resume Improvement (max 3 loops)
* 📈 Confidence Score Prediction
* ⚡ Conditional AI workflow using LangGraph

